                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The vampire nettle is adjacent to a creature taking persistent bleed damage</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The vampire nettle's central stalk dips into the wound and drinks blood. The vampire nettle gains 2d6 temporary Hit Points for 1 hour. The creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 1 hour if it fails a @Check[fortitude|dc:18] save (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2} on a critical failure).</p>"
