                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A living humanoid that dies while under the effects of alluring scent rises as a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.pathfinder-monster-core.Actor.Zombie Shambler] after [[/gmr 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}. The zombie isn't controlled by the vampire nettle but typically remains in the area to guard the plant for [[/gmr 1d4 #days]]{1d4 days} before wandering off. At some point within 1 week after leaving, the zombie collapses, and a new, fully grown vampire nettle erupts from its chest.</p>"
